
{ Bold

A ~bold~ word.

~Bold~: abc def.

~Bold~, too.

This is ~bold~, as well.

Why isn't everything ~bold~?

This should be ~bold~!

}

{ Italic

An *italic* word.

*Italic*: abc def.

*Italic*, too.

This is *italic*, as well.

Why isn't everything *italic*?

This should be *italic*!

}

